s, chaque individu devant répondre de ce qu’il aura accompli.","en":"And those who believed and whose descendants followed them in faith - We will join with them their descendants, and We will not deprive them of anything of their deeds. Every person, for what he earned, is retained.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","fr":"Et ceux qui","en":"And those who","tr":"wa-alladhīna","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"ءَامَنُوا۟","fr":"a cru","en":"believed","tr":"āmanū","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"وَٱتَّبَعَتْهُمْ","fr":"et suivi eux","en":"and followed them","tr":"wa-ittabaʿathum","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"ذُرِّيَّتُهُم","fr":"leur descendance","en":"their offspring","tr":"dhurriyyatuhum","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"بِإِيمَـٰنٍ","fr":"dans foi","en":"in faith","tr":"biīmānin","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"أَلْحَقْنَا","fr":"Nous va joindre","en":"We will join","tr":"alḥaqnā","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"بِهِمْ","fr":"avec eux","en":"with them","tr":"bihim","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"ذُرِّيَّتَهُمْ","fr":"leur descendance","en":"their offspring","tr":"dhurriyyatahum","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"وَمَآ","fr":"et non","en":"and not","tr":"wamā","isWaqf":false},{"position":10,"ar":"أَلَتْنَـٰهُم","fr":"Nous va priver eux","en":"We will deprive them","tr":"alatnāhum","isWaqf":false},{"position":11,"ar":"مِّنْ","fr":"de","en":"of","tr":"min","isWaqf":false},{"position":12,"ar":"عَمَلِهِم","fr":"leurs actions","en":"their deeds","tr":"ʿamalihim","isWaqf":false},{"position":13,"ar":"مِّن","fr":"(dans) tout","en":"(in) any","tr":"min","isWaqf":false},{"position":14,"ar":"شَىْءٍۢ ۚ","fr":"chose","en":"thing","tr":"shayin","isWaqf":false},{"position":15,"ar":"كُلُّ","fr":"Chaque","en":"Every","tr":"kullu","isWaqf":false},{"position":16,"ar":"ٱمْرِئٍۭ","fr":"personne","en":"person","tr":"im'ri-in","isWaqf":false},{"position":17,"ar":"بِمَا","fr":"pour ce que","en":"for what","tr":"bimā","isWaqf":false},{"position":18,"